        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK23">
<l>irumai vakaiterin tīṇṭaṟam pūṇṭār</l>
<l>perumai piṟaṅkiṟ ṟulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The greatness of those who have discovered the properties of both states of being, and renounced the world, shines forth on earth (beyond all others).</l>
            </lg>
